<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-Kütüphanem</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;900&family=Merriweather:wght@700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #D1D5DB; }
        .serif-font { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="m-0 p-0 overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="bg-black text-white h-14 flex items-center justify-between px-4 sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <span class="font-black text-xl tracking-tighter">E-Kütüphanem</span>
            <div class="relative flex items-center">
                <input type="text" class="rounded-full py-1 px-4 pr-10 text-black text-sm w-64 outline-none border-2 border-transparent focus:border-purple-500" placeholder="Ara...">
                <button class="absolute right-0 bg-[#7B1FA2] p-1.5 rounded-r-full hover:bg-purple-800 transition-colors">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer">
                <span class="text-lg">🌐</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold">Türkçe</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 ml-1">TR</span>
            </div>
            <button class="bg-[#FFC107] text-black text-xs font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-sm shadow-[inset_0_-2px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:bg-yellow-500">Oturum Aç</button>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-xl items-center">
                <span class="text-red-600 hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer">▶️</span>
                <span class="text-blue-600 hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer font-bold">f</span>
                <span class="text-red-500 hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer">📌</span>
                <span class="text-yellow-400 hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer">👻</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="flex">
        <aside class="w-60 bg-[#C0C0C0] min-h-screen p-3 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border-r border-gray-400 shadow-xl">
            <button class="bg-[#E91E63] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">📖</span> Romantik Kitap
            </button>
            <button class="bg-[#1976D2] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">🎓</span> Akademik Kitap
            </button>
            <button class="bg-[#00BCD4] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">💡</span> Kişisel Gelişim
            </button>
            <button class="bg-[#FF9800] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">🧸</span> Çocuk Kitapları
            </button>
            <button class="bg-[#F44336] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">📚</span> Edebiyat Kitabı
            </button>
            <button class="bg-[#3F51B5] text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-black/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-black/10 p-1 rounded">🧠</span> Psikoloji Kitabı
            </button>
            <button class="bg-black text-white text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-sm text-[11px] font-black flex items-center gap-2 border-b-4 border-white/20 mt-4 hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all">
                <span class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded">🏠</span> E-Kütüphanem
            </button>
        </aside>

        <main class="flex-1 p-12">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
                
                <div class="w-full md:w-80 flex-shrink-0">
                    <div class="relative group">
                        <div class="w-full h-[450px] bg-gray-800 shadow-[20px_20px_60px_#bebebe,-20px_-20px_60px_#ffffff] border-4 border-white rounded-sm overflow-hidden relative">
                             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543005139-0599607bb585?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-6">
                                <span class="text-white font-black text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest leading-none">Alacakaranlık</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-300 text-xs mt-1">Stephanie Meyer</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex justify-between mt-6 p-3 bg-white/40 border border-black/5 rounded shadow-inner">
                        <span title="Sepete Ekle" class="text-xl cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">🛒</span>
                        <span title="Yazdır" class="text-xl cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">🖨️</span>
                        <span title="Paylaş" class="text-xl cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">📶</span>
                        <span title="Bağlantı" class="text-xl cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">🔗</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-black text-white py-4 text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-3 shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                        <span class="text-lg">➕</span> Add to My E-Library
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="flex-1">
                    <h1 class="text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-1 leading-none serif-font">Psychology</h1>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm mb-6 tracking-tight">By Stephenie Meyer</p>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 bg-black/5 p-2 rounded w-fit px-4 border border-black/5">
                        <span class="text-[#FFC107] text-2xl tracking-tighter">★★★★☆</span>
                        <span class="text-sm font-black text-gray-800">4.5 <span class="text-gray-400 font-normal ml-1">(4536 ratings)</span></span>
                    </div>

                    <article class="text-sm text-gray-800 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-justify font-medium max-w-2xl border-l-2 border-black/10 pl-6 italic">
                        <p>
                            Üç şeyden kesinlikle emindim. Birincisi, Edward bir vampirdi. İkincisi, onun bir parçası mı ve bu parçasının ne kadar baskın olabileceğini bilmediğim bir yanı -kana susamışlığı- vardı. Ve üçüncüsü, ona koşulsuz ve geri dönülemez bir şekilde aşıktım.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Porselen teni, altın gözleri, büyüleyici sesi ve doğaüstü yetenekleriyle Edward hem karşı konulmazdı hem de gizemliydi. Şimdiye kadar pek çok kimliğini gizli tutmayı başarmıştı; ancak Bella onun karanlık sırrını çıkarmaya kararlıydı. 
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <div class="mt-16 flex items-center justify-center gap-16">
                        <button class="text-5xl hover:text-[#7B1FA2] transition-colors active:scale-90 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100">⬅️</button>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-400"></div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#7B1FA2] animate-pulse shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/50"></div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-400"></div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="text-5xl hover:text-[#7B1FA2] transition-colors active:scale-90 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100">➡️</button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mt-10 border-x-8 border-black py-4 px-12 text-center bg-white/10">
                        <p class="font-black italic text-gray-900 text-2xl uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">
                            "Binlerce Kitap Tek Tıkla Yanında"
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-[11px] font-black text-gray-500 uppercase mt-1 tracking-widest">Roman, kişisel gelişim, akademik ve daha fazlası...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
